Ask HN: Get first users (in this case)
text:
Hi! It's not a tech question but a question about go to market.

A brief background: I have been a big fan of finance/markets, but I have been in a "reader" mode only (not a "writer"). I have been thinking about a solution that could be helpful to many people. But the problem is that I don't have a big audience to launch it today (for the reason I explained). I tried to launch on subreddits, but the anti-spam filters banned my posts.

So, how can I launch a product when at the moment I don't know many people?

Show HN: Herbs Assist – Open-Source AI Assistant for Microservices Developement
text:
Hello HN community, we just released Herbs Assist, an open source AI assistant that helps developers create use cases and specs using OpenAI GPT-3 Codex.

It simplifies the workflow by generating natural language specs and Herbs specs and use case files based on the information provided.

We are looking for feedback and suggestions for improvements. Since it is also open source, contributions are welcome.
